---
title: White Chocolate Mousse Pots with Berry Compote & Crumble Topping | Serves 4
description: Creamy, dreamy and decadent, round out your night with these heavenly white chocolate pots. Leave them with enough
time to set in the fridge, then top with some berry compote and buttery crumble for the crunch factor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66016b9ecf720b0a31b8bcf8-bb54091c-3180100b.jpeg
